metadata.name: PATHWAY
metadata.description:
Part of the 'ICELAND_Wanderer.Within' 6-piece collection.

PATHWAY, a moment captured on a trail within an ice-cave. This was shot during mid-day so the sun was beaming down directly over the ice-caps creating an extremely bright and ethereal glow into the cavern.
